  "title": "Account Manager/ Sales Manager (Basic up $6500/ Audio Visuals)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Salary:</strong> Up to $6,500 basic + Commission<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Mon–Fri, 9:00 am – 6:00 pm<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Kallang</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop new business opportunities and manage existing accounts.</li><li>Generate leads through prospecting, networking, social media, and marketing activities.</li><li>Conduct market research to understand client needs and sales potential.</li><li>Arrange and attend client meetings, prepare presentations, and pitch solutions.</li><li>Prepare quotations, negotiate pricing, and follow up on purchase orders.</li><li>Liaise with suppliers, vendors, and partners to secure competitive terms.</li><li>Represent the company at meetings, pitches, and industry events.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years of relevant sales experience in Audio Visuals Industry.</li><li>Strong communication, negotiation, and relationship-building skills.</li></ul><p><strong>How to Apply</strong><br />Submit your CV via “Apply Now” or text <strong>+65 9422 1220</strong> for a confidential discussion.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>MTC Consulting Pte Ltd | 15C7752<br />EA Reg. No.: R22111807 | Yap Teng Hui</p>",
